contentrichtext.text: '''M50''' or '''M-50''' may refer to: In '''transportation''': * [[M-50 (Michigan highway)]], a state highway in Michigan * [[M50 motorway (Great Britain)]], a motorway in England * [[M50 motorway (Ireland)]], a motorway in Ireland * [[BMW M50]], a 1989 automobile piston engine * [[Suzuki Boulevard M50]], a 800cc V-twin muscle cruiser by Suzuki Motor Company * The FAA identifier of [[Boardman Airport]] in Boardman, Oregon In '''art''': * [[50 Moganshan Road]] (M50), Shanghai's contemporary art district In '''science''': * [[Messier 50]] (M50), an open star cluster in the constellation Monoceros In '''military equipment''': * [[M50 Joint Service General Purpose Mask]], United States military gas mask * [[M50 Super Sherman]], an Israeli tank * [[M50 Reising submachine gun]], an American submachine gun * [[M50 Ontos]], an American tank destroyer * [[Madsen M-50]], a Danish submachine gun * [[Myasishchev M-50]] 'Bounder', a Soviet bomber {{Letter-NumberCombDisambig}}
